@precedenceguo  thank you for your reply. I had that error when I debug on CPU local machine. When I run the code on GPU cluster, no errors. Maybe it just not working on CPUs.

However I got another problem. The code works fine for the first several hundreds of iterations. Then it stops due to GPU out of memory (~10GB). I minimized the input image size but not helping. Why the GPU memory usage is unstable? The VOC07 dataset has no considerably large images.

Regards

@vchuravy I just did some update on [DTypeBN](https://github.com/Godricly/mxnet/tree/DTypeBN). However there are some issues to be fixed.
- different mean and variance type in fp16 for cudnn and mshadow
- fp16 mshadow BN seems not working
